<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MentorLink - Connect. Learn. Grow</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #003049;
      --secondary-color: #0077b6;
      --accent-color: #2a9d8f;
      --light-color: #e8f6fc;
      --surface-color: #ffffff;
      --muted-text: #60717a;
      --surface-border: #d9eaf2;
      --surface-soft: #f6fbfd;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.12), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.10), transparent 30%),
        #fbfeff;
    }

    .page-shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
    }

    .page-shell .container {
      max-width: min(1680px, calc(100vw - 40px));
    }

    .navbar {
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 14px 0;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--secondary-color) !important;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .navbar-brand img {
      margin-right: 10px;
      border-radius: 14px !important;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.12);
    }
    .nav-link {
      color: var(--primary-color) !important;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 0 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px !important;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      position: relative;
    }
    .nav-link:hover,
    .nav-link.active {
      color: var(--secondary-color) !important;
      background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.08);
    }

    .btn-nav,
    .btn-hero,
    .social-btn {
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
    }
    .btn-nav:hover,
    .btn-hero:hover,
    .social-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-nav.btn-outline-primary,
    .btn-hero.btn-outline-primary,
    .social-btn.btn-outline-primary {
      border-color: #bfdbe9;
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      background: white;
    }
    .btn-nav.btn-primary,
    .btn-hero.btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), #005f89);
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 22px rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.18);
    }

    .hero {
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding: 90px 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.16), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.08) 0%, rgba(232, 246, 252, 0.88) 46%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.95);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.10);
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      right: -70px;
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.07);
      transform: rotate(18deg);
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -40px;
      bottom: -80px;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.08);
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-grid {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-copy {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--secondary-color);
    }
    .hero .lead {
      font-size: 1.16rem;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-note {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.95);
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.06);
    }
    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 18px 0 0 24px;
    }
    .mentor-scene {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 470px;
    }
    .mentor-panel {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.95);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.10);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .mentor-panel.primary {
      top: 28px;
      right: 0;
      width: min(100%, 440px);
      padding: 22px;
    }
    .mentor-panel.secondary {
      left: 0;
      bottom: 18px;
      width: min(74%, 310px);
      padding: 18px;
    }
    .mentor-panel .panel-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.08);
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .conversation-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .avatar-stack {
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 22px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.12);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .avatar-mentor {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), #005f89);
    }
    .avatar-mentee {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color), #1f877b);
    }
    .conversation-meta strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .conversation-meta span {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }
    .message-bubble {
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .message-bubble.mentor {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.10), rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.04));
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      margin-right: 28px;
    }
    .message-bubble.mentee {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.12), rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.05));
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
      margin-left: 44px;
    }
    .progress-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .progress-chip {
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 12px 10px;
      background: #f7fbfd;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .progress-chip strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .progress-chip span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .journey-mini {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .journey-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--accent-color));
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    section {
      margin: 34px auto;
      padding: 78px 0;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: var(--surface-color);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.06);
    }

    .section-soft {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248, 252, 254, 0.98) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 100%);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: -10px;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 76px;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--accent-color));
    }
    .section-intro {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .feature-card,
    .step-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 30px 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.05);
      height: 100%;
      transition: all 0.28s ease;
    }
    .feature-card:hover,
    .step-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.10);
      border-color: #b9ddeb;
    }
    .role-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 30px 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.05);
      height: 100%;
      transition: all 0.28s ease;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .role-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.10);
      border-color: #b9ddeb;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.10), rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.12));
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .role-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 68px;
      height: 68px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.08);
    }
    .role-badge.mentee {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.12), rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.24));
      color: var(--secondary-color);
    }
    .role-badge.mentor {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.12), rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.24));
      color: var(--accent-color);
    }
    .role-badge.organization {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244, 211, 94, 0.22), rgba(244, 211, 94, 0.38));
      color: #9c7400;
    }
    .feature-card h5,
    .step-card h5 {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .role-card h5 {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .feature-card p,
    .step-card p {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .role-card p {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .role-list {
      padding-left: 0;
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .role-list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .role-list i {
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--accent-color));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 22px rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.18);
    }
    .journey-track {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .journey-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      padding: 24px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.05);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .journey-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--accent-color));
    }
    .journey-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.10), rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.12));
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .journey-card h5 {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .journey-card p {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 26px 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.05);
      text-align: left;
    }
    .testimonial-card p {
      color: var(--muted-text);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .testimonial-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .testimonial-avatar {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .testimonial-avatar.one {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), #005f89);
    }
    .testimonial-avatar.two {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color), #1f877b);
    }
    .testimonial-avatar.three {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f4b942, #e39d16);
    }
    .testimonial-meta strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .testimonial-meta span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted-text);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .contact-card {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--surface-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 34px 26px;
    }
    .contact-card p,
    .contact-card a {
      color: var(--muted-text);
    }
    .contact-card a {
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer {
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      padding: 22px 0;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 234, 242, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.05);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(26px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    .fade-in-up {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    }

    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.9rem;
      }
      .hero-copy {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-visual {
        padding: 20px 0 0;
      }
      .mentor-scene {
        min-height: 420px;
      }
      .mentor-panel.primary {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        top: 0;
      }
      .mentor-panel.secondary {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        left: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }
      .journey-track,
      .testimonials-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-shell .container {
        max-width: calc(100vw - 20px);
      }
      .navbar {
        border-radius: 18px;
      }
      .hero {
        padding: 72px 0;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.35rem;
      }
      .mentor-scene {
        min-height: auto;
      }
      section {
        padding: 58px 0;
      }
      .btn-hero {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 10px 0 0;
      }
      .journey-track,
      .testimonials-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-fluid page-shell px-3 px-lg-4">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light sticky-top">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#home">
          <img src="/images/Logo 1.png" alt="MentorLink Logo" width="50" height="50">
          MentorLink
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link smooth-scroll" href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link smooth-scroll" href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link smooth-scroll" href="#features">Features</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link smooth-scroll" href="#how-it-works">How it works</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link smooth-scroll" href="#contact">Contacts</a></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ms-lg-3 mt-3 mt-lg-0">
            <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-nav me-2">Sign up</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-nav">Login</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="home" class="hero text-center">
      <div class="container hero-content">
        <div class="row hero-grid g-4 justify-content-between">
          <div class="col-lg-6 hero-copy">
            <div class="hero-note fade-in-up">
              <i class="bi bi-compass"></i>
              Mentorship made clearer, simpler, and more human
            </div>
            <h1 class="fade-in-up">Connect. <span>Learn.</span> Grow.</h1>
            <p class="lead fade-in-up">
              MentorLink brings mentors, mentees, and organizations together in one structured platform built for meaningful guidance, practical growth, and long-term collaboration.
            </p>
            <div class="fade-in-up">
              <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-hero px-4 py-3 me-lg-2">Get Started</a>
              <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-hero px-4 py-3">Join as a Mentor</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 hero-visual">
            <div class="mentor-scene fade-in-up">
              <div class="mentor-panel primary">
                <div class="panel-label">
                  <i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill"></i>
                  Live Mentorship Moment
                </div>
                <div class="conversation-row">
                  <div class="avatar-stack avatar-mentor"><i class="bi bi-person-workspace"></i></div>
                  <div class="conversation-meta">
                    <strong>Mentor Session</strong>
                    <span>Career guidance, feedback, and growth planning</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="message-bubble mentor">
                  Let's break your goal into small steps. We can start with your profile, then prepare for your next session.
                </div>
                <div class="message-bubble mentee">
                  That helps a lot. I needed a clearer direction and someone to show me what to improve first.
                </div>
                <div class="progress-strip">
                  <div class="progress-chip">
                    <strong>1:1 Match</strong>
                    <span>Personalized guidance</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="progress-chip">
                    <strong>Feedback</strong>
                    <span>Clear next steps</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="progress-chip">
                    <strong>Progress</strong>
                    <span>Track growth over time</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mentor-panel secondary">
                <div class="conversation-row mb-2">
                  <div class="avatar-stack avatar-mentee"><i class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill"></i></div>
                  <div class="conversation-meta">
                    <strong>Mentee Journey</strong>
                    <span>From uncertainty to confident action</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="journey-mini"><span class="journey-dot"></span><span>Discover a mentor aligned with your goals</span></div>
                <div class="journey-mini"><span class="journey-dot"></span><span>Schedule sessions and receive guidance</span></div>
                <div class="journey-mini"><span class="journey-dot"></span><span>Build confidence through steady progress</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

